snippet.title: Clash- Artifacts of Chaos |Gameplay Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Zenozoik, a world quite unlike any other. Explore this strange land as Pseudo, a hermit living on the fringes of a society that obeys one law, the ritual.

You'll encounter strange creatures, starting with the boy, whose mysterious powers are the catalyst for an adventure that will change everything for the two of them. 

Clash: Artifacts of Chaos will be available in November 2022 on Xbox Series X|S & Xbox One.
#IDatXbox #IDXbox
